divs: Sighting DetailsMy Nephew took two almost consecutives pictures to the clouds. When he downloaded those pictures he realized about an object on the right side above the cables in the second shot. Pay my attention a hole in the clouds that appear in the second photograph, it does not appear in the previous shot. We do not know what is that object. those photographs where taken in Buenos Aires , Argentina ,Ciudad de Isidro Casanova ( Isidro Casanova Town).
Summary: Object appear in a photograph after download it on the computer.
